Package: beaconstools
Title: Building, Evaluating and Ranking Ecological Benchmarks
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Marc", "Edwards", , "me1@uablerta.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0800-8002")),
    person("BEACONs Project", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
    )
Description: Impliments the BEACONs toolbox in R. Ecological
    Benchmarks are built by calling the BUILDER software. Benchmarks can
    then be ranked based on their ecological representation relative to a
    reference area, and based on a range of other ranking metrics.
